WEBVTT

00:01.383 --> 00:02.884
<i>When I was a child,</i>

00:03.122 --> 00:06.519
<i>my favorite story was about</i>
<i>a man who lived forever,</i>

00:07.587 --> 00:09.016
<i>but whose eyes</i>
<i>were heavy</i>

00:09.018 --> 00:12.081
<i>with the weight</i>
<i>of all he'd seen,</i>

00:12.083 --> 00:15.646
<i>a man who fell</i>
<i>from the stars.</i>

00:17.000 --> 00:23.074
Advertise your product or brand here
